---
title: Turkey Samosa-Style Pockets with Mango Chutney and Fresh Salad
description: Earthy and spice-filled Indian flavours come alive in this recipe! This meal is inspired by samosas, the popular Indian street snack. Ground turkey is cooked with a fragrant spice mix, peas and potatoes, then gets tucked inside a pizza dough pocket and baked until steaming and crispy.
